---

<section
  id="about"
  class="px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-page py-section-gap border-y border-outline-variant bg-canvas"
>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-16 items-center">
    <div
      class="w-full md:w-1/3 aspect-[4/5] rounded-xl overflow-hidden"
    >
      <img
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        src={portrait}
        alt="A striking portrait of a modern software engineer in a minimalist studio environment."
      />
    </div>
    <div class="w-full md:w-2/3">
      <h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg mb-stack-md">Hey! I'm Majd.</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6 max-w-2xl">
        <p
          class="font-body-md text-body-md leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant"
        >
          I am a software engineer and Framer creator dedicated to scaling
          startups through clean code and intentional user experience. My work
          bridges the gap between technical architecture and visual storytelling.
        </p>
        <p
          class="font-body-md text-body-md leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant"
        >
          I believe in minimalist brutalism—where functionality dictates form
          and precision is the highest decoration. From complex backend systems
          to fluid motion design, I build tools that feel as good as they look.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4 pt-4">
          <span class="text-outline-variant">/</span>
          <a
            class="text-primary hover:underline font-ui-text text-[16px] font-bold"
            href="#contact">GET IN TOUCH</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
